ActAeronautics Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canadian Aviation Security Regulations, 2012 (Non-Passenger Screening — Phase 1)
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN AVIATION SECURITY REGULATIONS, 2012 (NON-PASSENGER SCREENING – PHASE I) in order to enable Canada to continue to meet the requirements of the more stringent International Civil Aviation Organization non-passenger screening standard by ensuring that every non-passenger entering the restricted area encounters a screening checkpoint.
